    {
        "content": "<p>Well you have to give the maths proof first -- lean does not do magic. To make progress here I suggest you ask a concrete question in maths, give a maths answer, and also give the question in lean formulated as a <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mwe.html\">#mwe</a> with a <code>sorry</code>. That is the best way to ask questions here. Right now your questions are too vague, you're just saying you have a complicated question without saying what it is.</p>",
        "id": 485472795,
